      <title>委内瑞拉政府和反对派重新团结以确定选举日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/venezuela-government-opposition-reunite-to-set-election-date</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着尼古拉斯·马杜罗进一步偏离去年达成的选举协议，委内瑞拉政府恢复与反对派的谈判，讨论总统选举的日期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/venezuela-government-opposition-reunite-to-set-election-date</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 18:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装势力蔓延至欧洲，印度柴油泛滥至亚洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indian-diesel-floods-to-asia-as-houthis-imperil-flows-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于胡塞武装对商船的袭击继续扰乱国际贸易，导致更多货物运往亚洲，本月迄今为止，从印度运往欧洲的柴油量降至 2022 年以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indian-diesel-floods-to-asia-as-houthis-imperil-flows-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 17:13:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于工人抗议薪酬，巴西央行推迟重要经济报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/brazil-central-bank-delays-key-economic-report-as-workers-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工作人员抗议要求加薪，巴西央行第二次推迟发布备受关注的经济学家调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/brazil-central-bank-delays-key-economic-report-as-workers-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京允许受制裁的世博银行收购汇丰银行俄罗斯分部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/putin-allows-sanctioned-expobank-to-buy-hsbc-s-russian-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 允许世博银行 (Expobank) 收购汇丰控股 (HSBC Holdings Plc) 在当地的子公司，让欧洲最大的银行在乌克兰入侵后退出俄罗斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/putin-allows-sanctioned-expobank-to-buy-hsbc-s-russian-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登愿意会见约翰逊讨论乌克兰和以色列援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/biden-willing-to-meet-johnson-to-discuss-ukraine-israel-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在白宫官员此前否认直接谈判的效用后，总统乔·拜登表示，他愿意与众议院议长迈克·约翰逊会面，讨论为乌克兰和以色列提供紧急资金方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/biden-willing-to-meet-johnson-to-discuss-ukraine-israel-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汉莎航空因 3.5 亿美元 ITA 交易面临欧盟警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/lufthansa-faces-eu-warning-shot-over-350-million-ita-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汉莎航空公司对意大利航空公司 ITA 航空公司的 3.25 亿欧元（3.5 亿美元）投资受到欧盟合并监管机构的威胁，除非它解决了监管机构将下达的一系列竞争问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/lufthansa-faces-eu-warning-shot-over-350-million-ita-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒂努布·艾德表示，尼日利亚央行必须更加“政治化”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/nigeria-central-bank-must-be-more-political-tinubu-aide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布的一名高级助手敦促央行关注其决定的政治影响，因为公众对近期经济改革的影响表示强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/nigeria-central-bank-must-be-more-political-tinubu-aide-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:01:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冯德莱恩寻求欧盟新任期并重点关注国防领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/von-der-leyen-seeks-new-eu-term-amid-ukraine-and-us-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩将增强欧盟的防御能力作为她争取第二次领导欧盟执行机构的关键焦点，因为欧盟正在努力应对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰和唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫等挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/von-der-leyen-seeks-new-eu-term-amid-ukraine-and-us-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:51:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳瓦尔尼遗孀会见欧盟，欧盟考虑对俄罗斯实施新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/navalny-widow-meets-eu-as-bloc-mulls-russia-sanctions-over-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的遗孀表示，她将继续与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京进行斗争，同时她会见了欧盟高级官员，考虑对克里姆林宫批评者之死实施新的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/navalny-widow-meets-eu-as-bloc-mulls-russia-sanctions-over-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:37:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称波兰边境封锁正在损害战争努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/ukraine-says-polish-border-blockade-is-affecting-its-war-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基辅的一名高级官员表示，波兰农民的边境封锁正在损害乌克兰的自卫能力，因为该国正在等待与俄罗斯作战的重要物资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/ukraine-says-polish-border-blockade-is-affecting-its-war-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:05:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
